text: Lycée Georges Clemenceau is a senior high school in Villemomble, Seine-Saint- Denis, France, in the Paris metropolitan area. The school opened in 1946 as an annex of Lycée Charlemagne (now Lycée Albert Schweitzer) in Le Raincy. On 1 January 1961 it became its own high school."Bref historique." Lycée Georges Clemenceau.
